ence-we-dont-trust-the-experts-anymore\">\"By Demanding Too Much from Science, We Became a Post-Truth Society\"</a>. <i>bigthink.com</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">6 August</span> 2018</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=bigthink.com&amp;rft.atitle=By+Demanding+Too+Much+from+Science%2C+We+Became+a+Post-Truth+Society&amp;rft.aulast=Hendricks&amp;rft.aufirst=Scotty&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbigthink.com%2Fscotty-hendricks%2Fthe-dark-side-of-popular-science-we-dont-trust-the-experts-anymore&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEasiness+effect\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Guardian_Carnall-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Guardian_Carnall_4-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20170722012836/https://www.theguardian.com/science/2017/feb/01/facts-are-the-reason-science-is-losing-in-the-current-war-on-reason-science-communication\">\"Facts are the reason science is losing during the current war on reason\"</a>. <i>The Guardian</i>. 2017-02-01. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number\" title=\"International Standard Serial Number\">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.worldcat.org/issn/0261-3077\">0261-3077</a>. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/science/2017/feb/01/facts-are-the-reason-science-is-losing-in-the-current-war-on-reason-science-communication\">the original</a> on 2017-07-22<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2017-02-06</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;