tiveness of Medical Research News in the Media\". <i>Science Communication</i>. <b>37</b> (2): 173\u2013189. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1177/1075547014556541\">10.1177/1075547014556541</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Science+Communication&amp;rft.atitle=How+Laypeople+Understand+the+Tentativeness+of+Medical+Research+News+in+the+Media&amp;rft.volume=37&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=173-189&amp;rft.date=2014-11-12&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1177%2F1075547014556541&amp;rft.aulast=Kimmerle&amp;rft.aufirst=Joachim&amp;rft.au=Flemming%2C+Danny&amp;rft.au=Feinkohl%2C+Insa&amp;rft.au=Cress%2C+Ulrike&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEasiness+effect\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite class=\"citation thesis\">Scharrer, Lisa (2013). <i>Why Ask an Expert if it's that Simple? The Easiness Effect of Science Popularization</i> (Ph.D thesis). M\u00fcnster: Westf\u00e4lische Wilhelms-University. <a href=\"/wiki/OCLC\" title=\"OCLC\">OCLC</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.worldcat.org/oclc/881617096\">881617096</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Adissertation&amp;rft.title=Why+Ask+an+Expert+if+it%27s+that+Simple%3F+The+Easiness+Effect+of+Science+Popularization&amp;rft.degree=Ph.D&amp;rft.inst=Westf%C3%A4lische+Wilhelms-University&amp;rft.date=2013&amp;rft_id=info%3Aoclcnum%2F881617096&amp;rft.aulast=Scharrer&amp;rft.aufirst=Lisa&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEasiness+effect\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw2206\nCached time: 20180920003206\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.164 second